          "context": "Bounded recent public-course multiplayer results. The discrete chart contains raw circuit points from Ascent Mode races only, ordered oldest to newest without a trend line or continuous-time implication; the exact table remains mixed-mode and newest first. All Courses uses short course names beneath graph columns. A single-course filter replaces repeated course names with concise local dates or times. If too few usable Ascent Mode races remain, omit the graph and retain the exact list. SHOW 6 MORE appends the next six rows from the already-fetched client-filtered collection, never requests server pagination, preserves scroll position, updates the shown count, resets to six when the course filter changes, and hides when all matching rows are visible.",
