      "context": "Focused study replacing the rejected visible CONTEXT/MEASURE grid. Four faceted-selection paths share one responsive grammar. Visible labels are self-explanatory; Race type, Record type, and Time Trial class exist only as visually hidden accessibility legends in component context. State is compatible with shareable query parameters. Selected options use a tonal field, heavier label, and a centered 3px amber rail inset 11px from the option boundary. Keyboard focus is a separate high-contrast cyan inset outline and may coexist with selection on another radio option.",
