      "context": "Accessible global-search dialog opened from the persistent header. Searches shallow public Gauntlets, Pilots, Teams, and Courses only. Catalogs load on first explicit search interaction; matching is client-side afterward. Deterministic order is exact label/tag, prefix, then substring/fuzzy, while groups remain separate. Arrow keys move between results, Enter activates, Escape closes, and focus remains trapped. No recent searches, popularity ranking, recommendations, fake latency, or analytics-dependent ordering.",
